  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/538a6365b33eec4dcb7a530ea8d26b03.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=497 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this dramatic and emotional romance, you'll experience a visual masterpiece as the story delves into coping with loss, facing change, and what it means to love another.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/c7f0f5750241fd70c13bbc5c085c884c.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=326 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When tragedy takes Shun's little sister away from him, he's left to try and cope with his survivor's guilt and move on, but his childhood friend takes a different approach. Wanting to see Shun smile, she puts her genius to work and creates a sentient android modeled after his dead sister.<br><br>Now faced with this innocent facsimile of your sister who's becoming a different person of her own, you're left to determine if you can love her all the same, or if you're better off moving on alongside either the friend who tried to bring her back for you or the friend who originally tried to accept the loss as well. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/32c59a2cdffefe422f9502457ea5da2b.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=326 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/6d696cfeed4cf813640980e0fb7864f8.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=450 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/90cd793deefedfd3be2fb7adbb139f2e.poster.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/90cd793deefedfd3be2fb7adbb139f2e.webm?t=1764611842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like minori's previous works, Trinoline utilizes countless CG, animated expressions, lip synch, and voice acting, along with careful, detailed production and direction to create a truly cinematic experience rarely found in visual novels.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/08cf43b461fb8d7e3d3bc5c6f48fe210.poster.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=496 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/08cf43b461fb8d7e3d3bc5c6f48fe210.webm?t=1764611842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience three unique, heart-wrenching stories full of romance, drama, and hardships.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/9e7f3f849cb49d52caf5394441c7ba75.poster.avif?t=1764611842\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/965010/extras/9e7f3f849cb49d52caf5394441c7ba75.webm?t=1764611842\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy numerous outstanding tracks composed by TENMON that bring the scenes to life and stick with you long after.</p></li></ul>",
